<workout_file>
  <author>Gravel God Training</author>
  <name>W01 Tue - FTP Test + Durability Markers</name>
  <description>• STRUCTURE:
  • 20 min warmup
  • 5 min all-out
  • 10 min recovery
  • 20 min max effort
  • 10 min easy
  • 10 min @ 85% of 20-min power (check HR drift)
  • 10 min cooldown

  • FTP test first—pace it right, sustained 20 minutes.
  • Then durability check: hold 85% of your 20-min power for 10 minutes and watch HR drift.
  • If HR rises &gt;5-8 bpm, you have durability limitations.
  • Write everything down.
  • FTP = 20-min avg × 0.95.</description>
  <sportType>bike</sportType>
      <workout>
    <Warmup Duration="1200" PowerLow="0.50" PowerHigh="0.75"/>
    <SteadyState Duration="300" Power="1.20"/>
    <SteadyState Duration="600" Power="0.55"/>
    <SteadyState Duration="1200" Power="1.05"/>
    <SteadyState Duration="600" Power="0.55"/>
    <SteadyState Duration="600" Power="0.85"/>
    <Cooldown Duration="600" PowerLow="0.70" PowerHigh="0.50"/>
  </workout>
